WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.300 align:start size:3% position:97% line:0%
♪

00:00:01.333 --> 00:00:07.473
A singular new design,
a reengineered chip, and 5G.

00:00:07.506 --> 00:00:11.144
This is iPhone 12 Pro.

00:00:11.177 --> 00:00:13.012
The vertical band
is precision-machined

00:00:13.045 --> 00:00:15.548
from stainless steel.

00:00:15.581 --> 00:00:17.550
The Ceramic Shield on the front

00:00:17.583 --> 00:00:21.354
is tougher than
any smartphone glass.

00:00:21.387 --> 00:00:22.655
And tighter borders allow

00:00:22.688 --> 00:00:26.159
for even larger
Super Retina XDR displays.

00:00:26.192 --> 00:00:28.561 align:start size:3% position:97% line:0%
♪

00:00:28.594 --> 00:00:32.832
5G is set to change the world
with radically faster speeds.

00:00:32.865 --> 00:00:35.001
The hardware and software
have been optimized

00:00:35.034 --> 00:00:38.504
for the best 5G experience.

00:00:38.537 --> 00:00:42.075
A14 Bionic has a smaller
five-nanometer transistor,

00:00:42.108 --> 00:00:44.877
which pushes the most powerful
chip in a smartphone...

00:00:44.910 --> 00:00:48.014
[RUMBLING]
...generations ahead.

00:00:48.047 --> 00:00:50.083
A new and improved
Pro camera system

00:00:50.116 --> 00:00:53.686
makes the 12 Pro
the photographer's iPhone.

00:00:53.719 --> 00:00:56.022
The larger iPhone 12 Pro Max

00:00:56.055 --> 00:00:58.257
takes these innovations
even further.

00:00:58.290 --> 00:00:59.592
[EXPLODING]

00:00:59.625 --> 00:01:02.895
Its bigger sensor dramatically
increases the detail captured

00:01:02.928 --> 00:01:06.532
and helps improve low-light
performance by 87 percent.

00:01:06.565 --> 00:01:08.201
[CAMERA SHUTTERS]

00:01:08.234 --> 00:01:10.369
[CRACKLING]
[SIZZLING]

00:01:10.402 --> 00:01:12.205
The custom-designed
LiDAR Scanner

00:01:12.238 --> 00:01:16.209
puts advanced-depth mapping
technology in your pocket.

00:01:16.242 --> 00:01:18.444
You can now take
a Night mode portrait

00:01:18.477 --> 00:01:20.713
and unlock a new world
of possibilities

00:01:20.746 --> 00:01:22.281
for augmented reality.

00:01:22.314 --> 00:01:24.217
[ENGINE REVVING]

00:01:24.250 --> 00:01:26.719
[CRUMBLING]

00:01:26.752 --> 00:01:29.388
iPhone 12 Pro
smashes the benchmark

00:01:29.421 --> 00:01:32.058
for highest-quality video
in a smartphone.

00:01:32.091 --> 00:01:36.129 align:start size:3% position:97% line:0%
♪

00:01:36.162 --> 00:01:38.064
And the movie industry
can now count on it

00:01:38.097 --> 00:01:40.733
as an essential piece
of equipment.

00:01:40.766 --> 00:01:43.102 align:start size:3% position:97% line:0%
♪

00:01:43.135 --> 00:01:46.472 line:0%
It is the world's first device
able to capture, playback,

00:01:46.505 --> 00:01:51.777 line:0%
and edit 10-bit HDR footage
with Dolby Vision.

00:01:51.810 --> 00:01:55.915
iPhone 12 Pro comes in two sizes
and in four finishes,

00:01:55.948 --> 00:02:00.486
including New Pacific Blue.

00:02:00.519 --> 00:02:03.990
An integral part of this year's
design is MagSafe,

00:02:04.023 --> 00:02:05.925
an intelligent system of magnets

00:02:05.958 --> 00:02:07.927
that connect accessories
in a whole new way.

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.762
[CLICKING]

00:02:09.795 --> 00:02:11.797
[CHARGING TONE]

00:02:11.830 --> 00:02:15.835
All this and more
make iPhone 12 Pro

00:02:15.868 --> 00:02:18.137
the most powerful iPhone ever.

00:02:18.170 --> 00:02:20.173 align:start size:3% position:97% line:0%
♪

